<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2014-12-31</DATELINE><TITLE>2 Application of Plastics in Medical Devices and Equipment</TITLE><BODY>This chapter will present a look at the medical device market with a particular focus on the materials of construction of devices and what we can expect in new products looking ahead. A deeper look at some other trends that have an effect on the direction of the medical device industry will be done. Finally, consideration will be given to a number of global factors that can have dramatic effects on our industry.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>